<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
<div class="box"><small>Effective date: <strong>October 6, 2025</strong></small></div>

<p>NOISEMAKER by DooWopp (“we”, “us”) explains how we collect, use, and protect personal information.</p>

<h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Account info:</strong> name, email, organization, plan tier.</li>
  <li><strong>OAuth data:</strong> TikTok user ID, access/refresh tokens, granted scopes, token expiry.</li>
  <li><strong>Content & metadata:</strong> captions, media URLs, schedules, status, analytics returned by APIs.</li>
  <li><strong>Technical:</strong> IP address, device/browser info, diagnostic logs, crash/error data.</li>
  <li><strong>Billing (if applicable):</strong> limited payment metadata from our processor (we don’t store full card numbers).</li>
</ul>

<h2>2. How We Use Data</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Authenticate with TikTok and perform actions you authorize (draft, schedule, post, fetch analytics).</li>
  <li>Operate, secure, and improve the App, including fraud and abuse prevention.</li>
  <li>Provide support, notify you about changes, and comply with legal obligations.</li>
</ul>

<h2>3. Data Sharing</h2>
<p>We do not sell your personal information. We share data only with:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Processors/Service Providers</strong> under contract (hosting, storage, analytics, error tracking, email, payments) bound to confidentiality and data-protection terms.</li>
  <li><strong>Legal/Compliance</strong> when required by law, to protect rights, safety, or prevent abuse.</li>
</ul>

<h2>4. Security</h2>
<p>We apply industry-standard controls (encryption in transit, restricted token access, secrets management, least privilege). No method is 100% secure.</p>

<h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
<ul>
  <li>OAuth tokens: kept while your account is active or until revoked/expired.</li>
  <li>Posting logs & analytics: typically 12–24 months for troubleshooting and reporting (subject to change; we honor deletion requests).</li>
  <li>Backups: time-limited rolling backups; deleted data may persist in backups for up to 30–90 days.</li>
</ul>

<h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
<p>Depending on your region (e.g., PIPEDA, GDPR/CCPA), you may have rights to access, correct, delete, export, or object to processing. Submit requests via <a href="./data-deletion.html">Data Deletion</a> or email us.</p>

<h2>7. International Transfers</h2>
<p>We may process data outside your country. Where required, we use appropriate safeguards (e.g., Standard Contractual Clauses).</p>

<h2>8. Children</h2>
<p>The App is not directed to children under 13 (or older age as required in your region). Do not use the App if you are under the minimum age.</p>

<h2>9. Changes</h2>
<p>We may update this Policy. Material changes will be posted with a new effective date.</p>

<h2>10. Contact</h2>
<p>Email: <a href="mailto:support@doowopp.com">support@doowopp.com</a><br>
Mailing Address: DooWopp, Toronto, ON, Canada (update with your legal address)</p>

